title: God Of War Resource Pack
briefDescription: This texture pack changes mostly items, and some other various things, based around the God Of War game series. This resource pack has been done ...

crawledImageUrls.text:
This texture pack changes mostly items, and some other various things, based around the God Of War game series. This resource pack has been done for a while, I just forgot to upload it. I will update it with more things from the game eventually.
The first thing this texture pack does is change all the names and textures of vanilla weapons to look like God Of War weapons, along with the shield.
Weapons from left to right (If you can?t see them from the picture:
Here you can see how the guardian shield looks (replaces how vanilla shield use to look)
This is what it looks like from the inside.

Since I wanted to have the leviathan axe be a feature in this resource pack, I re-textured the trident and changed the model. This allows you to throw and hit with the leviathan axe, plus the loyalty enchantment is similar to the recall abilities of the leviathan axe in the game.
I also changed the crosshair to look like how it does in God Of War 4 when you are aiming. I may also change the health eventually to look more like the game, depending on if anyone wants it.
